<!doctype html><html><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html;charset=utf-8"/><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1"><title>Ed Hatrick Smith - Web: designer / developer / problem solver</title><meta name="description" content="Ed Hatrick-Smith: Empire Tavern project"/><meta name="keywords" content="web developer, desginer, photographer, awesome person, solutions"/><meta name="author" content="Edward Hatrick-Smith: ed.hatricksmith@gmail.com"/><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/styles.projects.min.css"/><?php $thisPage="work";?><?php include_once("/home/akolob/public_html/analyticstracking.php") ?></head><body><?php include("/home/akolob/public_html/header.php");?><div id="projects"><h1 class="works_heading">Empire Tavern Facebook competition</h1><p class="breadcrumbs"><em><a href="/work/work.php">Work</a> / Empire Tavern</em></p><article><p class="projects_first">With a recent refurbishment, the <a href="http://www.empire.co.nz/" target="_blank">Empire Tavern</a> was eager to focus greater attention on their marketing as well as develop a strong Facebook community. I was tasked with tidying up their Facebook page, producing a competition app, as well as a few other assets.</p><p>These end result draws some of it's aesthetic from existing collateral such as menus. However, I did generally simplify things for web use and made the typography a tad more sophisticated. </p><p>I also suggested we produce a printed display item for use in bar with a QR code that would link to the competition on Facebook. All-in-all a simple but effective project.</p></article><section><h2 class="works_heading">Project Images</h2><div id="container" class="project_width"><a class="fancybox gallery" href="/images/works/projects/empire/image_01_lge.jpg"><div class="project project_sm"><img src="/images/works/projects/empire/image_01_sml.jpg" alt="Facebook comp. non-fans"><div class="caption fade-caption"><h3 class="element_title">Enlarge</h3></div></div></a><a class="fancybox gallery" href="/images/works/projects/empire/image_02_lge.jpg"><div class="project project_sm"><img src="/images/works/projects/empire/image_02_sml.jpg" alt="Facebook comp. fans"><div class="caption fade-caption"><h3 class="element_title">Enlarge</h3></div></div></a><a class="fancybox gallery" href="/images/works/projects/empire/image_03_lge.jpg"><div class="project project_sm"><img src="/images/works/projects/empire/image_03_sml.jpg" alt="In-bar display flyer"><div class="caption fade-caption"><h3 class="element_title">Enlarge</h3></div</div></a><a class="fancybox gallery" href="/images/works/projects/empire/image_04_lge.jpg"><div class="project project_sm"><img src="/images/works/projects/empire/image_04_sml.png" alt="760x120 web banner"><div class="caption fade-caption"><h3 class="element_title">Enlarge</h3></div></div></a></div><div class="clearfix"></div></section></div><div class="clearfix"></div><?php include("/home/akolob/public_html/footer.php");?><script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.9.0/jquery.min.js"></script><script src="/js/jquery.projects.min.js" ></script><script type="text/javascript">$(".fancybox") .attr('rel', 'gallery') .fancybox({padding : 0 ,minWidth : 215 ,maxWidth : 900 ,autoSize : true ,maxHeight : 600 ,});</script><script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.9.0/jquery.min.js"></script><script src="/js/jquery.isotope-min.js"></script><script type="text/javascript">$(function(){var $container=$('#container');$container.isotope({itemSelector: '.project'});});</script></body></html>